### 使用说明 / Notes
### 1. 先运行登录接口，复制返回结果里的 token。
### 2. 把 token 粘贴到下面的 adminToken 或 userToken。
### 3. 再运行 /me 或 /admin/** 接口。

@adminToken = paste_admin_token_here
@userToken = paste_user_token_here

### 注册用户 / Register user
POST http://localhost:8080/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "spring01",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 登录管理员 tom，获取 ADMIN token / Login as admin
POST http://localhost:8080/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "tom",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 登录普通用户 alice，获取 USER token / Login as normal user
POST http://localhost:8080/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "alice",
  "password": "abc123"
}

### 不带 token 访问 /me，应该失败 / Access /me without token
GET http://localhost:8080/me

### 假 token 访问 /me，应该失败 / Access /me with invalid token
GET http://localhost:8080/me
Authorization: invalid-token

### 带 ADMIN token 查看自己 / Access /me with admin token
GET http://localhost:8080/me
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### 带 USER token 查看自己 / Access /me with user token
GET http://localhost:8080/me
Authorization: {{userToken}}

### 普通用户修改自己的密码 / Change my password
PUT http://localhost:8080/me/password
Authorization: {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "alice",
  "password": "abcdef"
}

### 管理员查询全部用户 / Admin get all users
GET http://localhost:8080/admin/users
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### 管理员查询单个用户 / Admin get user
GET http://localhost:8080/admin/users/tom
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### 管理员重置用户密码 / Admin reset password
PUT http://localhost:8080/admin/users/tom/password
Authorization: {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "tom",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 管理员删除用户 / Admin delete user
DELETE http://localhost:8080/admin/users/spring01
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### USER token 访问管理员接口，应该失败 / USER access admin API should fail
GET http://localhost:8080/admin/users
Authorization: {{userToken}}

### 参数校验失败：用户名为空，密码太短 / Validation error
POST http://localhost:8080/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "",
  "password": "123"
}
